Diagnostic trace: L1 prefix cache never accumulates across requests
====================================================================

Workload: 5 identical p=512 prefill requests on Gemma 4 E2B 4-bit, gen=1,
direct decode (--disable-ngram-acceleration), --prefill-chunk 2048, against
a single ax-engine-server process started by scripts/cpu_trace_prefill.py.

Diagnostic eprintln was temporarily added to:
  crates/ax-engine-mlx/src/runner.rs::probe_runner_snapshot_for_prefix
  crates/ax-engine-mlx/src/runner.rs::store_prompt_prefix_snapshots
recording cache.entries.len() and key fields. Reverted after this trace
was captured; this artifact is the entire record of the smoking gun.

Captured 2026-05-18.

